        "workflow: rg -n \"repair_and_validate_queues\\(|maintain_and_save_loaded_queues|create_undo_snapshot\" crates/ralph/src/queue/loader crates/ralph/src/commands/run/parallel crates/ralph/src/commands/run/supervision crates/ralph/src/cli/machine/queue_docs.rs -g '*.rs' :: found mutating runtime repair calls and only explicit machine queue repair creating undo."
